# CalibreMCP ğŸ“š

**FastMCP 2.0 server for comprehensive Calibre e-book library management through Claude Desktop**

[![FastMCP](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastMCP-2.0-blue)](https://github.com/jlowin/fastmcp)
